column2: SELECT TOP # sp.objid, sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.modelMag_u, sp.modelMag_g, sp.modelMag_r, sp.modelMag_i, sp.modelMag_z, sp.modelMagErr_u, sp.modelMagErr_g, sp.modelMagErr_r, sp.modelMagErr_i, sp.modelMagErr_z  FROM SpecPhoto sp  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) n  ON sp.objID=n.objID  WHERE (sp.class=&&&)
